  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t11/11日又是停戰紀念日了，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我覺得在對待這個日子的態度上，很能夠分辨文明和野蠻。上海以前有一個停戰紀念日的紀念碑，給日本帝國拆了，<br/>\n<br/>\r\n香港多年以來一直紀念這個日子<br/>\n<br/>\r\n好多年前有過英國官員去北京，北京的官員對poppy表達了不滿<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmVlZWMzOTliNmZkMTlmZTliMDQ4LnBuZz93aWR0aD05NDUmaGVpZ2h0PTU5NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/beeec399b6fd19fe9b048.png?width=945&amp;height=595\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/beeec399b6fd19fe9b048.png?width=945&amp;height=595\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/beeec399b6fd19fe9b048.png?width=945&amp;height=595\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMzhmN2E0NTY2ZWYyNTYyMTAzNDVkLmpwZz93aWR0aD04MDAmaGVpZ2h0PTQ5NQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/38f7a4566ef256210345d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=495\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/38f7a4566ef256210345d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=495\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/38f7a4566ef256210345d.jpg?width=800&amp;height=495\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNWI4ZjdiZTU4MTMzOWEwMmYzZDk3LmpwZz93aWR0aD02ODQmaGVpZ2h0PTEwMjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5b8f7be581339a02f3d97.jpg?width=684&amp;height=1020\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5b8f7be581339a02f3d97.jpg?width=684&amp;height=1020\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/5b8f7be581339a02f3d97.jpg?width=684&amp;height=1020\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZjdiOTFiMmI1ZTUyN2IwNWNkOGRkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f7b91b2b5e527b05cd8dd.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f7b91b2b5e527b05cd8dd.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/f7b91b2b5e527b05cd8dd.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDBkNzM2YTc5ZDJiNTYxYWY2ZjJkLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xOTIwJmhlaWdodD0xMDgw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/00d736a79d2b561af6f2d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/00d736a79d2b561af6f2d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/00d736a79d2b561af6f2d.jpg?width=1920&amp;height=1080\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDRkNmUzMzdjYjU4ZjkyZTk5OTEyLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD03MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/44d6e337cb58f92e99912.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/44d6e337cb58f92e99912.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/44d6e337cb58f92e99912.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n來自電影Empire of the Sun <br/>\n<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly95b3V0dS5iZS9uNjhrRnBvY3l0Yz9zaT1ONDJYZk5hZWpvRmh3T2xuJnQ9MTc3\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://youtu.be/n68kFpocytc?si=N42XfNaejoFhwOln&amp;t=177\">上海，二戰結束時</a><br/>\n<br/>\r\n和很多描述的戰爭勝利了不一樣，戰爭的勝利顯得如此蒼白和空虛\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
